<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About BlogSpace</h1>
    <p>Discover our story, our mission, and what drives us forward.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; margin-bottom: var(--space-16);">
  <div class="article-content" style="max-width: 100%;">
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-10);">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80" alt="Our Team" style="border-radius: var(--radius-xl); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);">
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: var(--font-size-3xl); margin-top: 0;">Our Story</h2>
    <p>BlogSpace started with a simple idea: creating a platform where stories matter. In a world cluttered with noise, we wanted to build a sanctuary for writers and readers alike. A place that prioritizes clean typography, beautiful white space, and a distraction-free environment. Since our inception, we have empowered thousands of independent writers to share their perspectives with the world without the friction of complex publishing tools.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);">Our Mission</h2>
    <p>Our mission is to democratize publishing while maintaining a premium, high-quality aesthetic. We believe that everyone has a story worth telling, and the tools to tell that story should be elegant, intuitive, and accessible. We strive to connect curious minds with profound ideas.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);">What We Stand For</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Simplicity:</strong> We strip away the unnecessary, leaving only what enhances the reading and writing experience.</li>
      <li><strong>Quality:</strong> From our code architecture to our design system, we pursue excellence.</li>
      <li><strong>Community:</strong> We believe in fostering a supportive, engaging, and inspiring community of creators.</li>
      <li><strong>Freedom:</strong> Authors retain full control over their words and their voice.</li>
    </ul>

    <div style="background: var(--color-primary-light); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: var(--space-10); text-align: center; margin-top: var(--space-12);">
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: var(--font-size-3xl); margin-top: 0; color: var(--color-primary);">Write With Us</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: var(--font-size-lg); margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">Have a story to tell? Join our growing community of writers and publish your first article today.</p>
      <a href="/dashboard/new" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Start Writing</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
